Scope
-----

This license covers the original source in this repository: the hand-written
runtime (`src/*.c`/`*.h` outside `src/gen/`), the recompiler-directive files
(`recomp/*.cfg`), tooling (`tools/`), and documentation (`docs/`, `DEBUG.md`,
`README.md`).

It does **not** cover, and grants no rights to:

- The ActRaiser ROM, or any content derived from it.
- `src/gen/*.c` and `recomp/funcs.h` — code mechanically recompiled from the
  ROM. These are never committed to this repository (see `.gitignore` and
  the README's "What can (and can't) be committed here" section); you
  generate them yourself, locally, from your own legally obtained ROM, and
  they remain subject to the original game's copyright regardless of this
  license.
- `snesrecomp-go/`, a Go reimplementation of the historical Python
  `snesrecomp` plus its copied C runtime and adapted documentation. The source
  repository had not declared an overall license at the snapshot used for the
  port. See `snesrecomp-go/ATTRIBUTION.md` and
  `snesrecomp-go/runtime/README.md` for provenance.
- `tools/oracle/libretro.h`, which contains and remains covered by the
  libretro project's own MIT license notice.

